The features of this product include:
- Augmented Reality interface
- Voice-controlled AI assistant
- Bluetooth connectivity
- UV and Blue Light filtering
- Wireless charging with extended battery life

The product comes with a user guide that covers various aspects from introduction, product overview, sizing and fit, to safety tips and troubleshooting.

The customer warranty includes a two-year limited warranty on all electronic components. They have a customer-friendly return policy with a 30-day return policy with no questions asked.

For any further queries or issues, customers can contact their support at support@contoso-galaxy-innovations.com. They also provide a FAQ section to resolve common issues.
